### Get all genres (default pagination)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/genres

### Get all genres (custom pagination)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/genres?page=2&limit=10

### Get genre by id
GET http://localhost:5000/api/genres/3

### Create genre (Success)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/genres HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "title": "New test genre"
}

### Update genre
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/genres HTTP/1.1
content-type: application/json

{
  "id": 20,
  "title": "Updated genre"
}

### Delete genre
DELETE  http://localhost:5000/api/genres/20 HTTP/1.1
